quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  38,52,Uye parutivi pavo pachave neQaasiraat-At-Tarf (madzimai anozvibata asingadi vamwe varume kunze kwevarume vavo chete) vemazera akaenzana
  38,53,Izvi ndizvo zvamunovimbiswa (imi vanotya Allah) pazuva rekutongwa
  38,54,"(Zvichanzi kwavari): Zvirokwazvo iyi iraramo yedu isingaperi"
  38,55,Zvakadaro! Uye avo vanopfurikidza mwero (vasingatendi) vachave nokudzokera kwakaipa (Moto)
  38,56,"Gehena! Mavachatsvira, uye inzvimbo yakaipa yekuzororera"
  38,57,Zvakadaro! Naizvozvo vasiyei varavire mvura inopisisa uye netsvina inobuda muzvironda
  38,58,Uye imwe (mitongo) yakafanana neuyu – yese pamwechete
  38,59,"Iri iboka ramuchapinda naro (muGehena), havana muchingamidzo! Zvirokwazvo, vachave vanotsva mumoto"
  38,60,"Ivo (vatevedzeri vevakarasika) vachati: “Uye nemi! Hakuna muchingamidzo kwamuri! Ndimi mava munounza izvi kwatiri (nekutirasisa kwenyu panyika), naizvozo iyi inzvimbo yakaipa kugara!”"
  38,61,"Vachati: “Tenzi vedu! Chero ani aunza izvi kwatiri, muwedzerei mutongo wakapetwa mumoto!”"
  38,62,"Uye vachati: “Dambudziko redu nderei, hatisi kuona vanhu vataiverengera pavaipi?”"
  38,63,"“Taivatora sechisekwa, kana kuti maziso edu arikutadza kuvaona?”"
  38,64,"Zvirokwazvo, ichi ichokwadi kupikisana kwevanhu vemumoto"
  38,65,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Ndingori muyambiri, uye hakuna mumwe mwari (ane kodzero yekunamatwa) kunze kwaAllah, Mumwechete, Samasimba.”"
  38,66,"“Tenzi vematenga nenyika uye nezvose zviri mazviri, vane simba rose, vanoregerera.”"
  38,67,"Iti: “(Iri Qur’aan) mashoko makuru.”"
  38,68,“Ayo amunofuratira!”
  38,69,“Ndakanga ndisina ruzivo rwemadzimambo epamusoro (ngirozi) pavaipikisana vachikurukura (nezvekusikwa kwaAdam).”
  38,70,"“Izvi zvave zvinodzikiswa kwandiri, kuti ini ndingori muyambiri ari pachena.”"
  38,71,"(Yeuka) apo Tenzi vako vakati kungirozi: “Muchokwadi, ndichava ndinosika munhu kubva muivhu.”"
  38,72,"“Naizvozvo kana ndamuumba zvakakwana uye ndikamufemera mweya wandakasika, mova munomupfugamira.”"
  38,73,Naizvozvo ngirozi dzakapfugama dzose
  38,74,"Kusara kwaDhiyabhorosi, akazvitutumadza uye akava umwe wevasingatendi"
  38,75,"(Allah) vakati: “Iwe Dhiyabhorosi! Chii chakudzivisa kubva mukupfugamira uyo wandasika nemaoko angu? Unozvitutumadza here kana kuti wava umwe wepamusoro-soro?”"
  38,76,"Iblees (Dhiyabhorosi) akati: “Ndiri nani pane iye. Makandisika kubva mumoto, uye mamusika kubva kuivhu.”"
  38,77,"(Allah) vakati: “Naizvozvo ibva muno! Zvirokwazvo, uri umwe weavo vakarasirirwa.”"
  38,78,“Uye zvirokwazvo kurengera kwangu kuchave pauri kusvika muzuva rokupihwa mubhadharo.”
  38,79,"Iblees (Dhiyabhorosi) akati: “Tenzi vangu! Ndipei kurarama (nguva) kusvika pazuva ravachamutswa (kubva kuvafi).”"
  38,80,"(Allah) vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, uri umwe weavo vakapihwa nguva (kurarama).”"
  38,81,“Kusvika pazuva renguva yakatarwa.”
  38,82,"Iblees (Satani)) akati: “Nesimba renyu, ndichavarasisa vose.”"
  38,83,“Kusara kwevaranda venyu vanotenda vamakasarudza pakati pavo.”
  38,84,"(Allah) vakati: “Chokwadi, chokwadi ndicho chandinotaura.”"
  38,85,“Ndichazadza Gehena newe (Satani) neavo vose kubva kwavari (vanhu) vanokutevera.”
  38,86,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Handikukumbirii mubairo pariri (Qur’an), uye handisi umwe wevanonyengedza.”"
  38,87,“(Qur’aan) iri ringori yeuchidzo kuAl-Aalameen (vanhu nemaJinn).”
  38,88,“Uye zvirokwazvo muchaona chokwadi charo mushure mekanguva.”
  39,1,"Zvakadzikiswa zveBhuku iri (Qur’aan) kubva kuna Allah, Samasimba, Vane huchenjeri hwese"
  39,2,"Zvirokwazvo, takadzikisa Bhuku kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) muchokwadi. Naizvozvo namata Allah (Vega) nekuita mabasa echitendero nemoyo wose uchifadza Allah"
  39,3,"Zvirokwazvo, chitendero ndecha Allah Voga. Uye avo vanotora vabatsiri kunze kwaAllah (vanoti): “Tinovanamata kuti vatiswededze pedyo naAllah.” Zvirokwazvo, Allah vachatonga pakati pavo maererana izvo zvavanopesana. Zvirokwazvo, Allah havatungamiriri uyo anonyepa, uye asingatendi"
  39,4,"Dai Allah vaida kuita mwana, vangadai vakasarudza wavaida pakati pevavakasika. Kurumbidzwa ngakuve kwavari! NdiAllah, Mumwechete, Samasimba"
  39,5,"Vakasika matenga nepasi muchokwadi. Vanoita kuti husiku hupinde muzuva uye vanoita kuti zuva ripinde muhusiku. Uye vakapa mutemo kuzuva nemwedzi. Chimwe nechimwe chinofamba (munzira ne) munguva yakatarwa. Zvirokwazvo, ndivo Samasimba, Vanoregerera zvikuru"
  39,6,"Vakakusikai kubva kumunhu mumwechete (Adam); uyezve vakasika mukadzi wake (Hawwa (Evha)) kubva kwaari (Adam). Uye vakava vanokutumirai zvipfuyo zvisere dziri zviviri zviviri (hwai yechirume neyechikadzi; mbudzi yechirume neyechikadzi; mombe yechirume neyechikadzi; ngamera yechirume neyechikadzi). Vanokusikai muzvibereko zvanaamai venyu, chisikwa mushure mechisikwa mumarima matatu. Ava ndiAllah, Tenzi venyu. Kwavari ndiko kune humambo. Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna chimwe chinhu chine kodzero yekunamatwa kunze kwavo). Naizvozvo, sei muchiitwa kuti mufuratire"
  39,7,"Mukasatenda, zvirokwazvo, Allah ndivo mupfumi pamusoro penyu. Havafadzwi nekusatenda kwevaranda vavo. Uye mukatenda, vanofadzwa nemi. Hakuna munhu achatakura mutoro wemumwe. Uye kuna Tenzi venyu ndiko kwamuchadzokera, uye vachava vanokuudzai zvamaiita. Zvirokwazvo, vanoziva zvikuru zviri mumoyo"